callOnAdaptor((address,bytes[])[]).details: There are several safety checks in this function to prevent strategists from abusing it.      - `blockExternalReceiver`      - `totalAssets` must not change by much      - `totalShares` must remain constant      - adaptors must be set up to be used with this cellarSince `totalAssets` is allowed to deviate slightly, strategists could abuse this by sending      multiple `callOnAdaptor` calls rapidly, to gradually change the share price.      To mitigate this, rate limiting will be put in place on the Sommelier side.
